<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>kk哥的博客 - 我的损友们</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --black: #0a0a0a;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --gray: #888888;
            --light-gray: #f5f5f5;
            --border: #e0e0e0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--white);
            color: var(--black);
            line-height: 1.8;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        /* 博客头部 */
        .blog-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .blog-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
        }

        .blog-header .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: var(--gray);
            font-weight: 400;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.2s forwards;
        }

        .blog-header .meta {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: var(--gray);
            margin-top: 15px;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.4s forwards;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* 博客文章样式 */
        .blog-post {
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.6s forwards;
        }

        .post-title {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.3;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 20px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--black);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .post-title:hover {
            border-left-color: var(--gray);
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }

        .post-meta {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: var(--gray);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .post-meta span {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 5px;
        }

        .post-content {
            font-size: 1.05em;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: var(--black);
        }

        .post-content p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .post-content .highlight {
            background: #ffffcc;
            padding: 2px 5px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .post-content .highlight:hover {
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--white);
        }

        /* 文章卡片 */
        .post-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
        }

        .post-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
        .post-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1s; }
        .post-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 1.2s; }

        .post-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-color: var(--black);
        }

        .post-card h2 {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: var(--black);
        }

        .post-card .date {
            font-size: 0.85em;
            color: var(--gray);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .post-card .excerpt {
            color: var(--gray);
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .post-card .read-more {
            color: var(--black);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .post-card .read-more:hover {
            gap: 10px;
            color: var(--gray);
        }

        /* 损友卡片 - 博客风格 */
        .friend-post {
            background: var(--light-gray);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--black);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
        }

        .friend-post:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }

        .friend-post:hover {
            transform: translateX(10px);
            box-shadow: -5px 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .friend-post h3 {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .friend-post .nickname {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: var(--gray);
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .friend-post .tags {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .tag {
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 5px 12px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .tag:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            background: var(--white);
            color: var(--black);
            border: 1px solid var(--black);
        }

        .friend-post p {
            color: var(--gray);
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        /* 故事列表 */
        .story-list {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .story-item {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--black);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
        }

        .story-item:hover {
            transform: translateX(8px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .story-item h4 {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: var(--black);
        }

        .story-item p {
            color: var(--gray);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .story-item .laugh {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            position: absolute;
            top: 15px;
            right: 15px;
            opacity: 0.3;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .story-item:hover .laugh {
            opacity: 0.8;
            transform: rotate(10deg);
        }

        /* 损友语录 - 引用样式 */
        .roast-section {
            background: var(--light-gray);
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 40px 0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 1.4s forwards;
        }

        .roast-section h2 {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--black);
        }

        .roast-quote {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--black);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .roast-quote:hover {
            transform: translateX(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .roast-quote .speaker {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--black);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        .roast-quote .quote {
            color: var(--gray);
            font-style: italic;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* 关系状态 - 列表样式 */
        .relationship-list {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .relationship-item {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--black);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
        }

        .relationship-item:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
        .relationship-item:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
        .relationship-item:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1s; }
        .relationship-item:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 1.2s; }

        .relationship-item:hover {
            transform: translateX(8px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .relationship-item h3 {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: var(--black);
        }

        .relationship-item p {
            color: var(--gray);
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        /* 对比区域 - 表格样式 */
        .comparison-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 1.6s forwards;
        }

        .comparison-table th,
        .comparison-table td {
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .comparison-table th {
            background: var(--light-gray);
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--black);
        }

        .comparison-table tr:hover {
            background: var(--light-gray);
        }

        .comparison-table td {
            color: var(--gray);
        }

        .comparison-table .score {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: var(--black);
        }

        /* 互动区域 */
        .interactive {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            margin: 40px 0;
            background: var(--light-gray);
            border-radius: 10px;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 1.8s forwards;
        }

        .interactive h2 {
            font-size: 1.4em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: var(--black);
        }

        .interactive p {
            color: var(--gray);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .interactive button {
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--white);
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin: 5px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .interactive button:hover {
            background: var(--white);
            color: var(--black);
            border: 1px solid var(--black);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* 博客导航 */
        .blog-nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: var(--light-gray);
            border-radius: 10px;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.8s forwards;
        }

        .blog-nav a {
            color: var(--black);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .blog-nav a:hover {
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--white);
        }

        /* 底部 */
        .blog-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            margin-top: 60px;
            color: var(--gray);
            font-size: 0.9em;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 2s forwards;
        }

        .blog-footer .tagline {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: var(--black);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* 响应式 */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .blog-header h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }

            .post-title {
                font-size: 1.5em;
            }

            .post-card h2 {
                font-size: 1.3em;
            }

            .comparison-table {
                font-size: 0.9em;
            }

            .comparison-table th,
            .comparison-table td {
                padding: 10px;
            }

            .blog-nav {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                gap: 10px;
            }
        }

        /* 特殊效果 */
        .shake {
            animation: shake 0.5s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes shake {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
            25% { transform: translateX(-5px); }
            75% { transform: translateX(5px); }
        }

        /* 加载动画 */
        .loader {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--white);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 9999;
            transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
        }

        .loader.hidden {
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .loader-content {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .loader-spinner {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border: 3px solid var(--border);
            border-top-color: var(--black);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
            margin: 0 auto 15px;
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        .loader-text {
            font-size: 1em;
            color: var(--gray);
        }

        /* 文章分隔线 */
        .post-divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--border);
            margin: 50px 0;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scaleX(0);
            animation: expandLine 0.8s ease forwards;
        }

        @keyframes expandLine {
            to {
                transform: scaleX(1);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- 加载动画 -->
    <div class="loader" id="loader">
        <div class="loader-content">
            <div class="loader-spinner"></div>
            <div class="loader-text">正在加载kk哥的博客...</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <!-- 博客头部 -->
        <header class="blog-header">
            <h1>kk哥的博客</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">记录生活 · 分享故事 · 展现真实的自己</div>
            <div class="meta">2026年 · 损友圈特辑</div>
        </header>

        <!-- 博客导航 -->
        <nav class="blog-nav">
            <a href="#about">关于我</a>
            <a href="#friends">损友故事</a>
            <a href="#quotes">语录</a>
            <a href="#relationship">关系</a>
        </nav>

        <!-- 文章：关于我 -->
        <article class="post-card" id="about">
            <h2>关于我</h2>
            <div class="date">2026-03-01 · 个人简介</div>
            <div class="post-content">
                <p>我是<span class="highlight">kk哥</span>，一个<span class="highlight">Dota2游廊开发工程师</span>。</p>
            </div>
        </article>

        <!-- 文章：兴趣爱好 -->
        <article class="post-card">
            <h2>我的兴趣爱好</h2>
            <div class="date">2026-03-01 · 生活记录</div>
            <div class="post-content">
                <p>我是一个<span class="highlight">苦逼牛马</span>。</p>
            </div>
        </article>

        <!-- 文章：损友故事（已隐藏） -->
        <!-- <article class="post-card" id="friends">
            <h2>我的损友们</h2>
            <div class="date">2026-03-01 · 损友圈特辑</div>
            <div class="post-content">
                <p>我有两位<span class="highlight">损友</span>，他们是我生活中不可或缺的一部分。</p>
            </div>

            <div class="friend-post">
                <h3>莫总</h3>
