        <!-- 损友内容显示按钮 -->
        <section class="interactive">
            <h2>想看损友内容吗？</h2>
            <p>输入对应的外号名字，解锁损友内容！</p>
            <div style="margin: 20px 0;">
                <input type="text" id="friendInput" placeholder="输入外号解锁内容" 
                       style="padding: 12px 20px; font-size: 1em; border: 2px solid var(--border); border-radius: 5px; width: 250px; margin-right: 10px;">
                <button onclick="unlockFriend()">解锁内容</button>
            </div>
            <div id="friendMessage" style="margin-top: 15px; color: var(--gray);"></div>
        </section>

        <!-- 损友内容显示区域（默认隐藏） -->
        <div id="friendContent" style="display: none;">
            <!-- 损友故事 -->
            <article class="post-card" id="friends">
                <h2>我的损友们</h2>
                <div class="date">2026-03-01 · 损友圈特辑</div>
                <div class="post-content">
                    <p>我有两位<span class="highlight">损友</span>，他们是我生活中不可或缺的一部分。</p>
                </div>

                <!-- 莫总 -->
                <div class="friend-post" id="mo-content" style="display: none;">
                    <h3>莫总</h3>
                    <div class="nickname">外号：人生导师（装逼版）</div>
                    <div class="tags">
                        <span class="tag">高高瘦瘦帅帅</span>
                        <span class="tag">严肃搞笑</span>
                        <span class="tag">千万级操盘手</span>
                        <span class="tag">13年老友</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>认识<span class="highlight">13年</span>的发小，表面上是<span class="highlight">千万级别抖音商家账号操盘手</span>，实际上是个<span class="highlight">严肃的搞笑担当</span>。</p>
                    <p>长得<span class="highlight">高高瘦瘦帅帅的</span>，但一开口就暴露了<span class="highlight">闷骚的本质</span>。总是一副<span class="highlight">"我懂人生"</span>的样子，其实内心戏超多。</p>
                    
                    <div class="story-list">
                        <div class="story-item">
                            <span class="laugh">😂</span>
                            <h4>年度最佳笑料：叫我妈叫姐</h4>
                            <p>今年过年他来我家做客，我妈跟他唠家常时，<span class="highlight">我妈发现</span>他居然要叫我妈叫<span class="highlight">"姐"</span>！更搞笑的是，连莫总自己都不相信，我当时就<span class="highlight">很难绷</span>，这辈分乱得我都想叫他<span class="highlight">"叔"</span>了。</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="story-item">
                            <span class="laugh">🤣</span>
                            <h4>人生导师的日常</h4>
                            <p>平时总是一副<span class="highlight">"我懂人生"</span>的样子，结果过年连辈分都搞不清楚。这就是<span class="highlight">千万级操盘手</span>的<span class="highlight">真实水平</span>？</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 啊猪 -->
                <div class="friend-post" id="zhu-content" style="display: none;">
                    <h3>啊猪（死人猪）</h3>
                    <div class="nickname">外号：死人猪（原名：小猪）</div>
                    <div class="tags">
                        <span class="tag">秃顶稀疏</span>
                        <span class="tag">闷骚怪</span>
                        <span class="tag">倒霉鬼</span>
                        <span class="tag">唱歌比我差</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>姓朱，刚认识时叫他<span class="highlight">"小猪"</span>，熟了就升级为<span class="highlight">"死人猪"</span>。一个<span class="highlight">稀疏的瘦子</span>，头顶<span class="highlight">"地中海"风格</span>。</p>
                    <p>性格是<span class="highlight">闷骚怪</span>，平时不说话，一说话就<span class="highlight">语出惊人</span>。更惨的是，他是个<span class="highlight">倒霉鬼</span>，每次跟他出门就没有好事情发生。</p>
                    
                    <div class="story-list">
                        <div class="story-item">
                            <span class="laugh">😅</span>
                            <h4>唱歌水平鉴定</h4>
                            <p>唱歌确实<span class="highlight">好听</span>，但比我差多了。每次KTV我都是<span class="highlight">麦霸</span>，他只能在旁边<span class="highlight">默默伴唱</span>。</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="story-item">
                            <span class="laugh">🤣</span>
                            <h4>倒霉鬼的日常</h4>
                            <p>每次跟他出门，不是<span class="highlight">丢东西</span>就是<span class="highlight">遇倒霉事</span>。我怀疑他是不是<span class="highlight">水逆体质</span>，建议他<span class="highlight">天天看黄历</span>。</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="story-item">
                            <span class="laugh">😂</span>
                            <h4>见面频率</h4>
                            <p>一年难见一面，每次见面都像是<span class="highlight">"久别重逢"</span>。不过虽然见面少，但<span class="highlight">损友</span>的<span class="highlight">感情</span>还在。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <!-- 损友语录 -->
            <article class="post-card" id="quotes">
                <h2>损友语录</h2>
                <div class="date">2026-03-01 · 经典语录</div>
                <div class="roast-section">
                    <div class="roast-quote" onclick="this.style.transform='scale(1.02)'; setTimeout(()=>this.style.transform='',300)">
                        <div class="speaker">莫总</div>
                        <div class="quote">"我今年25岁，应该叫你妈叫姐"</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="roast-quote" onclick="this.style.transform='scale(1.02)'; setTimeout(()=>this.style.transform='',300)">
                        <div class="speaker">啊猪</div>
                        <div class="quote">"我今天又倒霉了，出门踩狗屎"</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="roast-quote" onclick="this.style.transform='scale(1.02)'; setTimeout(()=>this.style.transform='',300)">
                        <div class="speaker">kk哥</div>
                        <div class="quote">"你们两个，一个装逼，一个倒霉"</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="roast-quote" onclick="this.style.transform='scale(1.02)'; setTimeout(()=>this.style.transform='',300)">
                        <div class="speaker">kk哥</div>
                        <div class="quote">"莫总，你还是叫我妈叫阿姨吧"</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <!-- 关系状态 -->
            <article class="post-card" id="relationship">
                <h2>关系状态</h2>
                <div class="date">2026-03-01 · 人际关系</div>
                <div class="relationship-list">
                    <div class="relationship-item" onclick="this.style.transform='translateX(10px)'; setTimeout(()=>this.style.transform='',300)">
                        <h3>🤝 莫总</h3>
                        <p>13年老友，人生导师（自称）</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relationship-item" onclick="this.style.transform='translateX(10px)'; setTimeout(()=>this.style.transform='',300)">
                        <h3>🐷 啊猪</h3>
                        <p>一年难见一面的损友</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relationship-item" onclick="this.style.transform='translateX(10px)'; setTimeout(()=>this.style.transform='',300)">
                        <h3>🎤 共同爱好</h3>
                        <p>唱歌（虽然水平不同）</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relationship-item" onclick="this.style.transform='translateX(10px)'; setTimeout(()=>this.style.transform='',300)">
                        <h3>😂 损友程度</h3>
                        <p>互相伤害，越损越亲</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <!-- 损友对比 -->
            <article class="post-card">
                <h2>损友对比</h2>
                <div class="date">2026-03-01 · 趣味对比</div>
                <table class="comparison-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>损友</th>
                            <th>总分</th>
                            <th>特点</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr onclick="this.style.background='var(--light-gray)'; setTimeout(()=>this.style.background='',300)">
                            <td>莫总</td>
                            <td class="score">8/10</td>
                            <td>装逼⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 搞笑⭐⭐⭐⭐ 靠谱⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr onclick="this.style.background='var(--light-gray)'; setTimeout(()=>this.style.background='',300)">
                            <td>啊猪</td>
                            <td class="score">6/10</td>
                            <td>倒霉⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 闷骚⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 唱歌⭐⭐⭐</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </article>

            <!-- 互动区域 -->
            <section class="interactive">
                <h2>想认识我的损友们吗？</h2>
                <p>点击按钮，看看你会遇到哪个"惊喜"！</p>
                <button onclick="showRoast('mo')">吐槽莫总</button>
                <button onclick="showRoast('zhu')">吐槽啊猪</button>
                <button onclick="showRoast('both')">一起吐槽</button>
            </section>
        </div>

        <!-- 留言板块 -->
        <article class="post-card" id="guestbook">
            <h2>留言板块</h2>
            <div class="date">2026-03-01 · 访客留言</div>
            <div class="post-content">
                <p>欢迎在下方留言！所有留言都会公开显示。</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- 留言表单 -->
            <div style="margin-top: 20px; padding: 20px; background: var(--light-gray); border-radius: 10px;">
                <div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    <input type="text" id="guestName" placeholder="你的名字" 
                           style="width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    <textarea id="guestMessage" placeholder="留言内容" rows="4" 
                              style="width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 5px; resize: vertical;"></textarea>
                </div>
                <button onclick="submitGuestbook()" style="padding: 12px 30px; background: var(--black); color: var(--white); border: none; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 500;">提交留言</button>
            </div>

            <!-- 留言列表 -->
            <div id="guestbookList" style="margin-top: 30px;">
                <h3 style="margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: 600;">留言列表</h3>
                <div id="guestbookMessages"></div>
            </div>
        </article>

        <!-- 底部 -->
        <footer class="blog-footer">
            <div class="tagline">爱咋咋地老子最吊</div>
            <p>kk哥的博客 · 2026年</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 页面加载动画
        window.addEventListener('load', function() {
            setTimeout(() => {
                document.getElementById('loader').classList.add('hidden');
            }, 1000);
        });

        // 解锁损友内容
        function unlockFriend() {
            const input = document.getElementById('friendInput').value.trim();
            const message = document.getElementById('friendMessage');
            const content = document.getElementById('friendContent');
            const moContent = document.getElementById('mo-content');
            const zhuContent = document.getElementById('zhu-content');

            // 重置显示
            moContent.style.display = 'none';
            zhuContent.style.display = 'none';

            if (input === '莫总') {
                moContent.style.display = 'block';
                content.style.display = 'block';
                message.innerHTML = '✅ 已解锁莫总的内容！';
                message.style.color = 'green';
            } else if (input === '死人猪' || input === '啊猪') {
                zhuContent.style.display = 'block';
                content.style.display = 'block';
                message.innerHTML = '✅ 已解锁啊猪（死人猪）的内容！';
                message.style.color = 'green';
            } else if (input === '全部' || input === 'all') {
                moContent.style.display = 'block';
                zhuContent.style.display = 'block';
                content.style.display = 'block';
                message.innerHTML = '✅ 已解锁全部损友内容！';
                message.style.color = 'green';
            } else {
                message.innerHTML = '❌ 输入错误！请输入正确的外号';
                message.style.color = 'red';
                content.style.display = 'none';
            }
        }

        // 互动按钮
        function showRoast(type) {
            const roasts = {
                mo: [
                    "莫总，你还是叫我妈叫阿姨吧！辈分都乱了！",
                    "千万级操盘手，连辈分都搞不清楚？",
                    "莫总，你这人生导师的水平有待提高啊！",
                    "13年老友，结果过年要叫我妈叫姐？"
                ],
                zhu: [
                    "死人猪，你今天又踩狗屎了吗？",
                    "秃顶不是你的错，但唱歌比我差就是你的不对了！",
                    "啊猪，你这倒霉体质什么时候能改改？",
                    "一年难见一面，见面就倒霉！"
                ],
                both: [
                    "莫总装逼，啊猪倒霉，绝配！",
                    "一个高高瘦瘦帅帅，一个稀疏秃顶瘦子，绝了！",
                    "人生导师和倒霉鬼，这就是我的朋友圈！",
                    "莫总叫我妈叫姐，啊猪出门踩狗屎，绝了！"
                ]
            };

            const randomRoast = roasts[type][Math.floor(Math.random() * roasts[type].length)];
            alert(randomRoast);
            
            // 添加抖动效果
            document.body.classList.add('shake');
            setTimeout(() => {
                document.body.classList.remove('shake');
            }, 500);
        }

        // 平滑滚动
        document.querySelectorAll('.blog-nav a').forEach(link => {
            link.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                const targetId = this.getAttribute('href');
                const targetElement = document.querySelector(targetId);
                if (targetElement) {
                    targetElement.scrollIntoView({
                        behavior: 'smooth',
                        block: 'start'
                    });
                }
            });
        });

        // 高亮文本点击效果
        document.querySelectorAll('.highlight').forEach(highlight => {
            highlight.addEventListener('click', function() {
                this.style.background = 'var(--black)';
                this.style.color = 'var(--white)';
                setTimeout(() => {
                    this.style.background = '#ffffcc';
                    this.style.color = 'var(--black)';
                }, 300);
            });
        });

        // 标签点击效果
        document.querySelectorAll('.tag').forEach(tag => {
            tag.addEventListener('click', function() {
                this.style.transform = 'scale(1.2)';
                setTimeout(() => {
                    this.style.transform = '';
                }, 200);
            });
        });

        // 留言功能 - 使用SQLite数据库
        async function submitGuestbook() {
            const name = document.getElementById('guestName').value.trim();
            const message = document.getElementById('guestMessage').value.trim();

            if (!name || !message) {
                alert('请填写姓名和留言内容！');
                return;
            }

            try {
                const response = await fetch('/api/guestbook', {
                    method: 'POST',
                    headers: {
                        'Content-Type': 'application/json'
                    },
                    body: JSON.stringify({ name, message })
                });

                const result = await response.json();

                if (result.success) {
                    // 清空表单
                    document.getElementById('guestName').value = '';
                    document.getElementById('guestMessage').value = '';

                    // 重新加载留言
                    await loadGuestbook();

                    // 显示成功消息
                    alert('留言成功！感谢你的留言！');
                } else {
                    alert('留言失败：' + result.error);
                }
            } catch (error) {
                console.error('提交留言失败:', error);
                alert('提交留言失败，请稍后重试');
            }
        }

        async function loadGuestbook() {
            const container = document.getElementById('guestbookMessages');
            container.innerHTML = '<p style="color: var(--gray);">正在加载留言...</p>';

            try {
                const response = await fetch('/api/guestbook');
                const data = await response.json();

                if (data.messages && data.messages.length > 0) {
                    let html = '';
                    data.messages.forEach((entry) => {
                        html += `
                            <div style="background: var(--white); padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--black); transition: all 0.3s ease;">
                                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                                    <strong style="color: var(--black);">${escapeHtml(entry.name)}</strong>
                                    <span style="color: var(--gray); font-size: 0.85em;">${entry.timestamp}</span>
                                </div>
                                <p style="color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">${escapeHtml(entry.message)}</p>
                            </div>
                        `;
                    });
                    container.innerHTML = html;
                } else {
                    container.innerHTML = '<p style="color: var(--gray);">暂无留言</p>';
                }
            } catch (error) {
                console.error('加载留言失败:', error);
                container.innerHTML = '<p style="color: red;">加载留言失败</p>';
            }
        }

        function escapeHtml(text) {
            const div = document.createElement('div');
            div.textContent = text;
            return div.innerHTML;
        }

        // 页面加载时初始化留言显示
        window.addEventListener('load', function() {
            loadGuestbook();
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>